info: Rating, 5 stars,  · November 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
- Great Host, friendly, communicative, quick to respond.
- Clean, safe and secure place.
- All amenities available as listed.
- Easy self check in.
- Daily cleaning service if required.
- Good neighbourhood, safe and peaceful.
- Easy to find (search by building name on map).
- Respectful staff/ security guard.
- Elevator running till late night.
- Restaurants within short distance, also food panda delivery service brings food at the door.
- Highly recommended.
